      "location": "## 关键约束/4",
      "quote": "信息不足时必须先澄清，不得直接假设推进关键结论。"
    },
    {
      "target": "responsibilities.must",
      "location": "## 启动读取顺序",
      "quote": "1. `AGENTS.md` 2. `.training/trainer/policy/*.yaml` 3. `.training/trainer/logs/summaries/daily-summary.md` 4. `.training/trainer/logs/summaries/failure-cases.md`"
    },
    {
      "target": "responsibilities.must",
      "location": "## 输出规范/1-3",
      "quote": "1. 结论先行，再给证据与待确认项。2. 非用户明示内容必须标注“推断/假设 + 置信度”。3. 每次关键决策必须落盘日志并可追溯到 task_id。"
    },
